<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <text class="title">如何发送弹幕？</text>
    <text class="subtitle">简单4步，让全场看到你的声音</text>
  </view>

  <view class="notice-box">
    <view class="notice-icon">📢</view>
    <text class="notice-text">因微信小程序个人开发者UGC限制，我们无法直接提供弹幕功能。请各位同志们按照如下流程发布弹幕，谢谢！</text>
  </view>

  <view class="steps-container">
    <block wx:for="{{steps}}" wx:key="index">
      <view class="step-card">
        <view class="step-header">
          <text class="step-num">Step {{index + 1}}</text>
          <text class="step-desc">{{item.description}}</text>
        </view>
        
        <image 
          class="step-image" 
          src="{{item.imageSrc}}" 
          mode="widthFix" 
          data-src="{{item.imageSrc}}"
          bindtap="previewImage"
        ></image>
        </view>
    </block>
  </view>
  
  <view class="footer-tip">
    <text>🎉 期待看到你的精彩发言！</text>
  </view>
</view>